{"tid":1357172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無知一問 咁依家星期六元朗仲出唔出？","createTime":"2019-07-23T16:14:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T16:56:30.000Z","uid":132310,"like":67,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1599137da51758d1e4d7e4fc8d6b26677be9256e","tid":1357172,"uid":132310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:14:24.000Z","msg":"<strong>一定去呀吊</strong><br />\n<br />\n唔去星期日屯元天一定無人敢出！<br />\n唔係搞人祠堂 我地去反恐呀<br />\n<br />\n好少開post<br />\n但嬲在啱啱同朋友傾<br />\n竟然都話唔知元朗去係為乜想唔出<br />\n又話牛屎佬真係打人架幫唔到咩手<br />\n依家要同大家講我地唔驚恐襲呀<br />\n係因為越少人出越易出事呀<br />\n和理非去先保護到前線 警察先無得再唔理呀<br />\n牛屎佬出黎打我啦<br />\n我死都保護屯元天既朋友出黎繼續發夢<br />\n<br />\n講咗好耐君妖個墳 上環開槍係唔可以忘記<br />\n但要對得知義士係 依家星期六日做啲咩呀<br />\n大家快啲幫手做多啲文宣唔該<br />\n唔好推沉行動post<br />\n要比大家知道去元朗唔係盲目復仇<br />\n要比大家知道和理非參加 係有咩重要性<br />\n星期六同星期日兩件事 快啲召集<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"8cd632429b56f0cbc61ebb300145d3baf5e883fa","tid":1357172,"uid":835,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:15:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rt9GdUA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRt9GdUA.gif&h=f3494e0b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aef628b73300828af852ed4887d26cd02b3de0c9","tid":1357172,"uid":132310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:15:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e4c42d7154ea20c278e660546bfa349eee417aa7","tid":1357172,"uid":271051,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:15:10.000Z","msg":"727 係和理非遊行"},{"pid":"b47bd1f1b80a9ef88b76e733b223d0181a08c106","tid":1357172,"uid":132310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:15:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e961e1ab3862a2c90da778063f03b2bc03e148d5","tid":1357172,"uid":132310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:15:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d8fb1fe9319b8f40623402c49a6ea63199dcba95","tid":1357172,"uid":174902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16: